==Starting out==
===Talking to Kit Breaker===
* '''Player:''' Hello, there!
* '''Kit Breaker:''' Hello! The name's Kit. Kit Breaker, at your service!
* '''Player:''' Kit? That's a nice name!
* '''Kit Breaker:''' Thank you! I chose it myself!
* '''Player:''' ... Thinking about it, I chose mine as well. I'm [player name], by the way.
* '''Kit Breaker:''' Very nice to meet you!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What brings you here?}}
** '''Player:''' What brings you here?
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Aha, glad you asked! It has been my recent lifelong dream to make a name for myself with the White Knights of Falador. It was part of the reason I chose my name, you know?
** '''Kit Breaker:''' I thought Sir Kit Breaker had a nice ring to it. The 'Sir' commands respect and sounds quite manly. I want people to think when they look at me: this man has it together.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Yet I've hardly set out and I'm already falling at the first obstacle. I have no equipment to call my own. I just dragged some heavy chests for hours and I'm puffed-out.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Worse, I don't even know exactly what's in them!
** '''Player:''' Sounds like you might need some help.
** {{tselect|Start the Pride event?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Let me help you out.
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' Oh, what a relief. Thank you, [player name].
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' I can't show myself to the White Knights like this. If I want to make a good first impression, I need to look the part. I'm pretty sure they don't bestow the title of Sir willy nilly.
*** '''Player:''' You could be right, I've not heard of any Sir Willy Nilly.
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' Anyway, I need a beard. I've done some research and all the best Sirs have one. I had a poster of Sir Tiffy Cashien in my room growing up and he's my inspiration.
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' But a beard isn't the only thing. I also need some armour! What kind of knight goes about without protection?
*** '''Player:''' Er, not sure I'm afraid.
*** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
*** {{topt|Talk about the beard.}}
**** '''Player:''' Tell me about the beard.
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' Well, as it turns out, I have yet to manage to grow a beard. Not for fault of trying, you know. I hear some people try their whole life and still can't.
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' It can't just be about genetics, since my dad's beard is glorious. Do you have any ideas?
**** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
**** {{topt|Wear a fake one?}}
***** '''Player:''' Wear a fake one?
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' I did consider that, and went as far as using my own hair clippings to make one when I shortened my hairstyle, but it was very itchy and not all that convincing.
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' Besides, I want to be true to myself, you know. If I can't grow the beard, wouldn't it just feel wrong?
***** {{tact|previous}}
**** {{topt|Ask a witch for a hair growth potion?}}
***** '''Player:''' Ask a witch for a hair growth potion?
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' I have seen the adverts, and I am preeeeetty sure that is a scam. I don't want to be one of those people that fall for them.
***** '''Player:''' That is fair.
***** {{tact|previous}}
**** {{topt|Visit the hairdresser?}}
***** '''Player:''' Visit the hairdresser? There's one not far from here in Falador.
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' I thought hairdressers only removed the hair, not added it.
***** '''Player:''' You'd be surprised. Technology has come a long way.
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' Hmm... Ok, I'm willing to give it a go. How does it work? I've been cutting my own hair at home this whole time, you see.
***** '''Player:''' I see! Normally you just turn up, but maybe I can get you an appointment?
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' You would? Oh thank you! I'll wait here for you!
***** {{tact|end}}
**** {{topt|Wait a few years?}}
***** '''Player:''' Wait a few years?
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' That's a long time to wait to find out there was a better way.
***** '''Player:''' Maybe this could be the fallback option if nothing else works?
***** '''Kit Breaker:''' I will consider it.
***** {{tact|previous}}
**** {{topt|Nevermind.}}
***** '''Player:''' Nevermind.
***** {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|Talk about the equipment.}}
**** '''Player:''' Tell me about the equipment.
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' Knights need armour. I will have more chance to be taken seriously if I am wearing some. Before I decide to take drastic measures and buy my own, I want to check the 'little something' my mum sent me out with.
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' See these chests?
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' They both make a very metallic sound when moved. I want to double-check whether there's equipment in there or not.
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' I don't have the right key though. I don't know if lockpicking is a skill that's well regarded among the white knights, but it's morally questionable. I would rather not risk it in case it harms my chances.
**** '''Kit Breaker:''' I know I hardly know you and all, but... Would you mind having a go at it for me? Please?
**** '''Player:''' Only because you asked nicely.
**** {{tact|end}}
*** {{topt|Nevermind.}}
**** '''Player:''' Nevermind.
**** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' Although I am not in a position to do that right now.
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' I understand. Let me know if you change your mind!
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|That's a lot of chests!}}
** '''Player:''' That's a lot of chests!
** '''Kit Breaker:''' They weigh as much as a dead dragon! I gained two Strength levels dragging them around. Why on Gielinor have we not yet come up with an easier way to carry things!
** {{tcond|If the player is an Ultimate Ironman:}}
*** '''Player:''' I know some people use banks, even though I don't personally.
** {{tcond|If the player isn't an Ultimate Ironman:}}
*** '''Player:''' Have you considered depositing your items in the bank?
** '''Kit Breaker:''' They wouldn't take these, apparently, and I can't even open them to empty them! They are locked and the key my mother gave me isn't the right one.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' I think the fact that she misplaced her glasses the other day has something to do with it.
** {{tact|previous}}

===Talking to Kit Breaker after starting the event===
