===Talking to the Hairdresser===
* '''Hairdresser:''' Good afternoon. In need of a haircut are we? Currently we're offering this service for free!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|event=no|I'd like a haircut please.}}
* {{topt|event=no|I'd like a shave please.}}
* {{topt|event=no|No thank you.}}
* {{topt|Do you offer appointments?}}
** '''Player:''' Do you offer appointments? An acquaintance of mine is trying to grow a beard and was thinking of coming here.
** '''Hairdresser:''' Normally, people come in and are served on a first come, first serve basis but I suppose I could book your friend in.
** '''Player:''' Yes please! Their name is Kit. Kit Breaker.
** '''Hairdresser:''' All done! They'll get a priority treatment as soon as they come in, as long as we're opened.
** '''Player:''' Thank you so much!
** '''Hairdresser:''' It's a pleasure!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Kit after booking an appointment===
* '''Kit Breaker:''' Hello again, [player name]!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|Talk about the beard.}}
** '''Player:''' I've put your name down for an appointment at the Falador hairdresser. He's expecting you at your earliest convenience.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Oh, so I could go now?
** '''Player:''' I suppose so.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Would you mind looking over my things while I'm gone? I promise I won't be long! Hopefully!
** '''Player:''' Ok then! Good luck!
** {{qact|Kit leaves for the hairdresser, and comes back with a new haircut.}}
** '''Player:''' Oh, where's the beard?
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Interesting story. The hairdresser was actually really helpful! We went through a few brochures of various hairstyles, he looked at my face structure.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' We tried a few styles, and it turns out the beard just wasn't me. But this new hairstyle? It's powerful yet manly.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' It is low-maintenance. It springs back up after taking a helmet off. I saw my face in the mirror and felt so good! What do you think?
** '''Player:''' Honestly, it seems to have boosted your confidence!
** {{tcond|If the player has not yet unlocked the heavy chest:}}
*** {{tact|previous}}
** {{tcond|If the player has already unlocked the heavy chest:}}
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' I'm really starting to look the part now! I just need some standard-issue weaponry and I'm good to go. Maybe it's time we unlocked the other chest.
*** '''Kit Breaker:''' Yes. I think the letter from my mom held the key to opening it. Let me know if you want me to read it to you again.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Talk about the equipment.}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|Nevermind.}}
** {{tact|above}}

