* '''Kit Breaker:''' We'll miss you, but this is your chance to go and find yourself out in the world. You'll always be welcome home but I get the feeling it might be a while before you're back.
* '''Kit Breaker:''' Never stop chasing your {{Colour|#0000ff|d}}reams. You've got a good heart and some... Decent armour to protect it with. Maybe look to replace it sooner rather than later.
* '''Kit Breaker:''' Kit's a great name too. I can't wait to hear the stories of Kit Breaker doing something h{{Colour|#0000ff|e}}roic - just don't be too brave all of the time.
* '''Kit Breaker:''' We love you lots. Mum. P.S. The dog misses you too.
* {{tact|end}}

===Upon opening the scuffed chest===
* '''Player:''' That's done! I'll let you check the contents out!
* '''Kit Breaker:''' My dad's old sword and shield! He definitely did not let me touch that before! Give me a second.
* {{qact|Kit equips the steel sword and kiteshield.}}
* '''Kit Breaker:''' I'm ready! I feel like I can take on the world! Let's go to see the White Knights, now!
* '''Player:''' What about your belongings? Are we taking them with us? Are you going to leave them here?
* '''Kit Breaker:''' I really don't want to bring them with me until I know for sure that I'm accepted. Hey, maybe I can ask one of the guards over there to keep an eye on them?
* '''Player:''' Why not?
* '''Kit Breaker:''' I tell you what. I'll go and ask, and if I don't come back, assume that he said yes and come and join me in the castle courtyard, ok?
* '''Player:''' Fair enough!
* {{qact|Kit leaves.}}
* '''Player:''' He's not coming back. I should head to the White Knights' castle courtyard.
* {{mes|Objective: Meet Kit near the squire, who is in the Falador Castle courtyard.|color=red}}
* {{tact|end}}

===Talking to Kit Breaker after opening the scuffed chest===
