** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|You should stay, you brought a lot with you.}}
** '''Player:''' You should stay, you brought a lot with you.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' I've only got most of my life in these containers.
** '''Player:''' See, past you believed in this! Present you should keep at it.
** {{qact|Kit's motivation increases by 15.}}
