** '''Player:''' Only if you don't give up though.
** '''Kit Breaker:''' With your belief I don't think I can give up!
** {{qact|Kit's motivation increases by 15.}}
** {{tact|continue}}
* {{topt|Say nothing.}}
** '''Kit Breaker:''' Do you not think I'll make it?
